## Installation

```sh
git clone ssh://git@stash.silabs.com/iot_software/zclip.js.git
cd zclip.js
npm install --production
```

## Development

Examples are located in `/examples`

```sh
var coap = require('coap');
var zcl = require('../.')(coap);

var onOff = new zcl.clusters.OnOff({
  ip: '::1',
  endpoint: 1
});

onOff.toggle();
```

